headline.print_headline: White House Party Crasher Fails to Make Ballot
headline.main: White House Party Crasher Fails to Make Ballot

lead_paragraph: One-time White House party crasher and former reality television figure Tareq Salahi has failed to submit enough valid signatures to qualify for the ballot as an Independent Green Party candidate for outgoing U.S. House Majority Leader Eric Cantor's seat in Congress.
